ygData.messageBody:
I didn't know know about Jojunga my last time in Innouthule, but being on
the continent i might head down there. My last expierence in Innouthule was
interesting, I took to arms with a lvl 14 Dark Elf Shadow Knight ( I was 14
at the time) and was in a duel to the death with her, I almost died, but I
succeeded and won the match. That is a hard area with all the troll bashers
around, so I would reccommend having a large group to kill the occasionial
troll that come about if you are 15+, Other than that, i dont know much
about the area, I tried to go get Ghoulsbane (Holy Sword) while there, got
lost in guk and then made my way out, all i know about Ghoulsbane is that it
is in lower guk on a high lvl Undead frogglok. May Tunare be with you

Laurana Highwind
